{"tid":1042968,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"脫北者組織千里馬民防 成立北韓流亡政府 矢言推翻「大惡」金正恩","createTime":"2019-03-02T02:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T03:55:01.000Z","uid":28765,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cc0d984dece381caef6f2180a8991dfd3c88f7","tid":1042968,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:07:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpo5MXsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpo5MXsT.jpg&h=736a0305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逃離北韓官民組成的「千里馬民防」組織，1日宣布成立北韓流亡政府，將矛頭直指金正恩（圖）政權。（彭博）<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-01 19:47<br />\n〔編譯孫宇青／綜合報導〕在外界聚焦北韓領袖金正恩與美國總統川普第二次會談破局之際，為金正恩兄長金正男之子金韓松（Kim Han Sol，譯音）提供庇護的「千里馬民防」組織，1日宣布成立北韓流亡政府，將矛頭直指金正恩政權，揚言傾全力推翻「大惡」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2713699_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2713699_1.jpg&h=b4ad2c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金正男前年2月疑似遭弟弟金正恩下令暗殺，其子金韓松此後由「千里馬民防」提供庇護。（美聯社檔案照）<br />\n<br />\n金正恩同父異母的兄長金正男，2017年2月在馬來西亞吉隆坡機場，遭VX神經毒劑暗殺身亡，元兇指向亟欲鞏固權力的金正恩。此後，由逃離北韓官民組成的「千里馬民防」（Cheollima Civil Defense）組織，開始為金正男之子金韓松提供庇護。<br />\n<br />\n「千里馬民防」在朝鮮半島爭取脫離日本殖民的「三一運動」100週年之際，於官網上以英文及韓文發表聲明，並上傳一支影片。在影片中，一名身穿黑白色韓服、臉部打上馬賽克的女子，在一座韓式傳統亭閣下朗讀聲明，宣布成立北韓流亡政府，名稱為「自由朝鮮」（Free Joseon）。<br />\n<br />\n聲明中批判北韓現行體制，指控政府主導思想統治、強制勞動等，主張「自由朝鮮」才是北韓人民唯一正統的代表，呼籲北韓人民起身對抗獨裁，「我們將獻身，以完全廢除玷汙人性靈魂的大惡，直至光明重臨平壤。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2713699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2713699&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C%2F7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=cba05cb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2713699&h=39ff8ca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2713699</a>"},{"pid":"6b0e85ac35aab58a1d5fc8903892e3304684b264","tid":1042968,"uid":84128,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"就算推翻到<br />\n都只係一個黑暗既政權換做另一個黑暗既政權"},{"pid":"ccda8b75cab2c441d2e6ae5c72795261bef158a5","tid":1042968,"uid":209890,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b0e85ac35aab58a1d5fc8903892e3304684b264","tid":1042968,"uid":84128,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:11:47.000Z","msg":"就算推翻到<br />\n都只係一個黑暗既政權換做另一個黑暗既政權"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:18:04.000Z","msg":"背後有美國佬照<br />\n美國佬d馬仔<br />\n唔係點敢起兵<br />\n邊個比錢"},{"pid":"b3b4c9bf70f1c43ecda021ea9428a7db14164825","tid":1042968,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T02:22:35.000Z","msg":"侵仔咁耐以黎提都冇提過金仔搵人暗殺佢大佬單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df52715bed98d3e67d3faa3229ecc843da38c33","tid":1042968,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"大韓民國已經係自稱正統代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e2d0885c0783bb073db47ccf6a336de86cd314","tid":1042968,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5df52715bed98d3e67d3faa3229ecc843da38c33","tid":1042968,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"大韓民國已經係自稱正統代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新北泡"},{"pid":"b90e6ff38ec02e2296277963adf210a83a42728c","tid":1042968,"uid":57554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:55:01.000Z","msg":"CIA ：岩岩大佬傾唔掂，你地可以開波。<br />\n<br />\n球棒同談判係要同時準備<br />\n呢個係好多仼美國總統都知"}]}